<m0>Inmates sue Nassau County<ql>
<m4>   LINE 1 IS .02 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m0>over unsafe jail conditions<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 2 IS 2.01 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS 1.236 INCHES<m2><ql>
